{"data":[{"date":"14:56 29/06","title":"Chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real v\u1ee5 sao Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/chi-62-trieu-bang-chelsea-vuot-mat-real-vu-sao-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Chelsea r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi The Blues. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois co mot tran dau xuat sac\" title=\"Courtois c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Liverpool-mua-Thibaut-Courtois-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Courtois ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Courtois kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin s\u1edf d\u0129 Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ramos-va-ronaldo-muon-real-mua-thu-mon-cua-chelsea-180-181590.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay Navas. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m, Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi kho\u1ea3ng 30 \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Alisson mua Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Courtois gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Liverpool-muon-mua-Nick-Pope-cua-Burnley-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a Roma kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Olympico \u1edf H\u00e8 2018: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Roma, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia. Theo \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Real, The Blues s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"718","checkdouble":"189942"},{"date":"15:00 29/06","title":"Ibrahimovic: \u201cTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/ibrahimovic-phat-bieu-ve-dt-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 3-0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 36 tu\u1ed5i cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ibrahimovic</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Euro 2016, Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat l\u1eebng danh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 62 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 116 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan. Nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 play-off. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Italia t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o VCK.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 18 WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 18 WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Ibrahimovic-phat-bieu-ve-Thuy-Dien-moi-vao-vong-18-WC-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T\u00a0Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u1ecdi Ibrahimovic tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. Sau c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Ibrahimovic l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t vui khi th\u1ea5y Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Ibrahimovic\" title=\"tien dao Ibrahimovic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/ibrahimovic-phat-bieu-ve-dt-thuy-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e2n hoan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d, Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, l\u00e1i xe \u0111i \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 c\u1edd t\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Mexico v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua \u0110\u1ee9c. Theo l\u1ecbch, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Janne Andersson s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf v\u00f2ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-messi-hay-cr7-ibra-chon-ra-cap-sao-se-toa-sang-o-world-cup-2018-421-188355.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Messi hay CR7, Ibra ch\u1ecdn ra c\u1eb7p sao s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thuy-dien-se-choi-tot-hon-khi-khong-con-ibrahimovic-421-188265.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/khong-lo-ibrahimovic-nhan-the-do-vi-gio-vo-voi-chu-lun-tai-my-331-186832.html\">Kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Ibrahimovic nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec gi\u1edf v\u00f5 v\u1edbi ch\u00fa l\u00f9n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibrahimovic-thua-nhan-dang-nho-mu-va-mourinho-172-185454.html\">Ibrahimovic th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111ang nh\u1edb MU v\u00e0 Mourinho</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"717","checkdouble":"189943"},{"date":"15:25 29/06","title":"Matic n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fred?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/matic-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-52-trieu-bang-mua-fred.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Trent Alexander Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAnh &ldquo;to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n&rdquo; nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 BHL \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ra l\u1ec7nh&rdquo; cho Tam S\u01b0 &ldquo;c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng&rdquo; gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Arnold &ndash; anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft World Cup c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arnold cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 thuy\u1ebft \u00e2m m\u01b0u n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 ngang nhau, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 Januzaj \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9\" title=\"Arnold\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/arnold.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Arnold cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Colombia 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o&rdquo; &ndash; Trent Alexander-Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e9 nh\u00e1nh t\u1eed th\u1ea7n, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Tam S\u01b0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp &ndash; h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129/Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh da ne duoc nhanh dau tu than ben trai\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu-421-189916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu-421-189916.html\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Eric Dier l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u!</span><br>\r\nEric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn thua tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca-421-189924.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca-421-189924.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9: Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u&hellip; tranh nhau nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 0-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"716","checkdouble":"189944"},{"date":"15:43 29/06","title":"Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec \"ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ea1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMorata \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Morata</span>, PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chelsea-muon-mua-Moussa-Marega-cua-Porto-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Morata \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Juventus ho\u1eb7c PSG ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Morata, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thay th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Fernando Llorente \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. Spurs \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n\u00a0m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Moussa Marega</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea va Tottenham muon co Marega\" title=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marega\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali \u0111\u00e3 ghi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u0110N, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Porto \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMoussa Marega r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, s\u00fat xa v\u00e0 ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarega c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro, song b\u00e1o ch\u00ed B\u0110N kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi ra 28 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton, West Ham v\u00e0 Schalke c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Marega, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"715","checkdouble":"189945"},{"date":"15:07 29/06","title":"HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 mang t\u00ean Josip Zeba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Croatia.</h2><h2>HAGL\u00a0th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c t\u00e2n binh\u00a0Josip Zeba cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n HAGL.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Josip-Zeba-HAGL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba\u00a0cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2, \"G\u1ed7\" \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t thay th\u1ebf c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh. Sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil Osmar thay th\u1ebf Rimario, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Kim Jin-seo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Josip Zeba sinh n\u0103m 1990, thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao 1m88 v\u00e0 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Slovenia trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o NK Aluminij (m\u00f9a r\u1ed3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 8 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Prva Liga 2018).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018, th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Josip Zeba th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V.League 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 HAGL s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ngay v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, khi 'G\u1ed7' c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda HAGL, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Josip Zeba.\u00a0CLB s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Josip Zeba v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Vincent Bossou \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\">HAGL m\u1ea5t C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League v\u00ec \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a V-League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"714","checkdouble":"189946"},{"date":"16:25 29/06","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \"bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3\" khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/sao-tre-tuyen-anh-vo-cung-buon-ba-khi-de-thua-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Trent Alexander Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAnh &ldquo;to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n&rdquo; nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 BHL \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;ra l\u1ec7nh&rdquo; cho Tam S\u01b0 &ldquo;c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng&rdquo; gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Arnold &ndash; anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft World Cup c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arnold cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 thuy\u1ebft \u00e2m m\u01b0u n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 ngang nhau, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 Januzaj \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9\" title=\"Arnold\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/arnold.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Arnold cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Colombia 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o&rdquo; &ndash; Trent Alexander-Arnold chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e9 nh\u00e1nh t\u1eed th\u1ea7n, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Tam S\u01b0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp &ndash; h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129/Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh da ne duoc nhanh dau tu than ben trai\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu-421-189916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu-421-189916.html\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Eric Dier l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u!</span><br>\r\nEric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn thua tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca-421-189924.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-01-bi-sieu-pham-giai-tri-va-niem-vui-chia-deu-cho-tat-ca-421-189924.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9: Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u&hellip; tranh nhau nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 0-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"713","checkdouble":"189948"},{"date":"16:15 29/06","title":"MU nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-hau-ve-trai-40-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Ryan Sessegnon c\u1ee7a Fulham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo The Times, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U nh\u1eafm Ryan Sessegnon n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Jose Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ashley Young \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m nay Young \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, M.U c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ef1u sao Aston Villa.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/5/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-hau-ve-trai-40-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ryan Sessegnon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Luke Shaw, song \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Luke Shaw \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, Mourinho c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Luke Shaw n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Young \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n Luke Shaw mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ryan Sessegnon \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 2000 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 Ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Fulham th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRyan Sessegnon c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 49 tr\u1eadn. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ryan Sessegnon b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Fulham b\u00e1n Ryan Sessegnon, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fulham nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/22/Hau-ve-Ryan-Sessegnon-bi-HLV-Fulham-canh-bao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Sessegnon mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-50-trieu-bang-mu-thoi-bay-moi-doi-thu-de-co-than-dong-anh-172-187645.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Ryan Sessegnon</span> c\u1ee7a Fulham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo The Times, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 18, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Craven Cottage.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"712","checkdouble":"189949"},{"date":"16:35 29/06","title":"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min c\u1ee7a Tottenham sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb Lyon b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3, The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Son Heung-Min</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop quan t\u00e2m Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Liverpool \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min thay Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min thay Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. Mua h\u1ee5t Nabil Fekir khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Metro, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min c\u1ee7a Tottenham sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb Lyon b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3, The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Son Heung-Min ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min om mat khoc sau tran thua Juventus\" title=\"Son Heung-min \u00f4m m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn thua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/son-heungmin-khoc-nuc-no-tottenham-xung-dang-gianh-chien-thang-truoc-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 Son Heung-min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc-172-189762.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Son Heung-Min</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. V\u1edbi Tottenham, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"711","checkdouble":"189950"},{"date":"16:35 29/06","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: center;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Philippines, L\u00e0o, Singapore v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Gap-hang-lom,-DT-U19-Viet-Nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-Trung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 3, 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00ec c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch quan chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, ho\u1eb7c ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng l\u00ean 'd\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n' cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thua Th\u00e1i Lan. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2017, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 Th\u00e1i Lan, Australia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c em khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia hay Philippines&quot;, \u00f4ng Tu\u1ea5n 'con' n\u00f3i th\u00eam.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 10 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen t\u1ea1i Surabaya tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110KV\u0110 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n l\u00fac 15h30 chi\u1ec1u 1/7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean VTV6)</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"710","checkdouble":"189953"},{"date":"16:51 29/06","title":"Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/7/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jasper Cillessen mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 1 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0\u00a01 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng anh \u1edf c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/10/ter-stegen-chan-thuong-cillessen-som-ra-mat-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jasper Cillessen \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 lu\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Marc-Andre ter Stegen khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Barca \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-thu-mon-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-liverpool-172-187430.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Kop l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1eeb 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, song t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cillessen v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"709","checkdouble":"189954"},{"date":"09:08 29/06","title":"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi sao s\u00e1ng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin \u2013 ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Nga \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow. M\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga. V\u00e0 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, Golovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0110T Nga. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb \u0111i b\u00f3ng, s\u00fat xa, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho t\u1edbi gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn m\u00ea m\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sao s\u00e1ng World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sao s\u00e1ng World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin khi chi \u0111\u1eadm</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sau khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft gh\u1ebf HLV</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tuy nh\u00ean, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Napoli v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea quy\u1ebft sa th\u1ea3i Conte m\u1eddi Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nConte v\u1eabn l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cao khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i CLB b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia. Trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Golovin, Conte kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi Granovskaia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Nga mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Alexey Smertin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Abramovich tin Golovin \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea-172-189734.html\">Hazard n\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri-172-189709.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n &ldquo;chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; HLV Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7-172-189593.html\">Chelsea ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"708","checkdouble":"189928"},{"date":"09:25 29/06","title":"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n tin vui khi \u201cMessi Iran\u201d b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110TQG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/messi-iran-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-dtqg-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Iran v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Sardar Azmoun \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch trong n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0110TQG v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p.</h2><h2>\"Messi Iran\"\u00a0Sardar Azmoun tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110TQG\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sardar Azmoun l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran \u1edf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat cao 1m86 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Nga cho CLB Rubin Kazan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi Iran Sardar Azmoun tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110TQG \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 23 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi Iran Sardar Azmoun tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110TQG \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 23 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/messi-iran-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-dtqg-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sardar Azmoun chia tay \u0110TQG v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c \u00e9p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sardar Azmoun l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o tuy\u1ec3n Iran v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, l\u00fac m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 b\u00e0n sau 36 tr\u1eadn cho tuy\u1ec3n Iran. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 11 b\u00e0n sau 14 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u2013 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup v\u1eeba qua, Sardar Azmoun \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Carlos Queiroz tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng su\u1ed1t trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ma R\u1ed1c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00f2n tuy\u1ec3n Iran b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Azmoun \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran l\u0103ng m\u1ea1, ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec7nh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00ed do ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 Sardar Azmoun quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T Iran.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sardar Azmoun chia s\u1ebb chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y tr\u00ean Instagram:\u00a0\u00a0\"Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 l\u0103ng m\u1ea1 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i l\u00e2m b\u1ec7nh nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i m\u1eebng khi m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nguy hi\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1eb9\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Azmoun c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e3nh di\u1ec5n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG Iran. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o trong su\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i tim t\u00f4i ao \u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i \u0111au trong su\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i v\u00ec t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 m\u00ecnh\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110TQG Iran hay kh\u00f4ng, song n\u1ebfu Azmoun kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau 6 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019. Iran v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat gi\u1ecfi, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-iran-11-bo-dao-nha-421-189644.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-iran-11-bo-dao-nha.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-iran-11-bo-dao-nha-421-189644.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Iran c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn gi\u00fap Seleccao gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-ve-cdv-nu-iran-tai-world-cup-2018-465-189631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/1368684.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-ve-cdv-nu-iran-tai-world-cup-2018-465-189631.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran khoe s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a C\u0110V n\u1eef Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o b\u1edfi v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef Iran, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-vat-va-vuot-qua-vong-bang-run-ray-cung-cr7-421-189582.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/bo-dao-nha-vat-va-vuot-qua-vong-bang-run-ray-cung-cr7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-vat-va-vuot-qua-vong-bang-run-ray-cung-cr7-421-189582.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: Run r\u1ea9y c\u00f9ng CR7</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Iran cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"707","checkdouble":"189930"},{"date":"09:46 29/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Real ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar gia nh\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tu-hao-chau-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Paris Saint-Germain.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Neymar. Nh\u1eefng Karim Benzema, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar. Ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG t\u1eeb Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p khi\u1ebfn anh c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Dani-Carvajal-chao-don-Neymar-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Neymar t\u1eeb PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Brazil d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Real \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, sau khi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil k\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018, ph\u00eda Real s\u1ebd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 350 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Carvajal mu\u1ed1n Neymar gia nh\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c CLB \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 si\u00eau sao 26 tu\u1ed5i. \u201cN\u1ebfu Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sinh ra \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Madrid, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Cadena SER.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar Carvajal\" title=\"Neymar Carvajal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/tu-hao-chau-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMadrid lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u00e9t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCarvajal \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Alvaro Odriozola, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real Sociedad. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh c\u0169ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Odriozola \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9\u201d, Carvajal n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Odriozola l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-real-sap-ban-ronaldo-180-189885.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Real s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/asensio-thua-nhan-kha-nang-roi-real-madrid-180-189770.html\">Asensio th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid-172-189735.html\">HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\">MU gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"706","checkdouble":"189932"},{"date":"11:11 29/06","title":"Samuel Umtiti: \"\u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Barcelona nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Messi<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 v\u1eady \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Samuel Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Samuel Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Samuel Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng sao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef1u chung l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Lionel Messi c\u1ee7a Argentina. Trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00ednh \"Leo\" l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Argentina l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina, Samuel Umtiti n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Barcelona: \"T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y anh \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t phi ph\u00e0m. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tuy\u1ec3n Argentina c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c\".</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t Messi kh\u00e1c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea5p c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng Barcelona nh\u01b0ng theo nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Messi ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vi\u00ean m\u00e3n. \"Leo\" v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng khi ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf l\u1edbn n\u00e0o cho x\u1ee9 Tango.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Umtiti c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Messi c\u1ee7a Barca c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Argentina: \"Anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Argentina. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 \u1edf Barcelona, l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u h\u1ecd v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina qu\u00e1 kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 30/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina-421-189897.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t Messi c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u1edf Argentina\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-co-vai-tro-tuong-tu-nhu-messi-421-189883.html\">Hazard c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-messi-gay-sot-voi-hanh-dong-don-tim-fan-cuc-dang-yeu-421-189845.html\">Video: Messi g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u201c\u0111\u1ed1n tim\u201d fan c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-21-vi-sao-messi-bi-xem-la-ke-phan-boi-421-189871.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 21: V\u00ec sao Messi b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/tiet-lo-noi-dung-doan-noi-chuyen-cua-messi-voi-dong-doi-trong-gio-nghi-465-189740.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 n\u1ed9i dung \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Messi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/marcos-rojo-trai-nghiem-tu-than-va-khoanh-khac-cuu-ca-dan-toc-389-189739.html\">Marcos Rojo: Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eed th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee9u c\u1ea3 d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"705","checkdouble":"189933"},{"date":"09:44 29/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n V-League b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u2018t\u1ee5t d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh\u2019 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH, HLV T\u00e0i Em m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m<br>\r\n</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL v\u00e0 SLNA v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 28/6, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi CLB. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cCLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft n\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f2n non ngh\u1ec1 \u1edf V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chuy\u1ec7n chia tay ngay sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1edd v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 r\u1ed3i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1ea3 quan trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra. Xin ch\u00fac anh em nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n theo d\u00f5i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh em trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Tu\u1ea5n Phong \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi: \u201cAnh em ai c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00ec sao ra n\u00f4ng n\u1ed7i n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m, s\u1ed1ng h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed3ng, vui v\u1ebb n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng anh em trong \u0111\u1ed9i. CLB n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 HLV Marian Mihail c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 mau ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"704","checkdouble":"189935"}]}